OL,6,FA serial shoplifter who stole high-
OL,7,Fvalue Jellycat toys, electric
OL,8,Ftoothbrushes, books, candles, and
OL,9,Fother goods has been jailed.
OL,11,FJason Thorpe, aged 54, of no fixed
OL,12,Faddress, targeted multiple shops
OL,13,Facross Sussex, including in Portslade,
OL,14,FHove and Brighton, between 9 August
OL,15,Fand 28 October.
OL,17,FThorpe entered Bert's Homestore in
OL,18,FHove on three occasions, each time
OL,19,Fleaving with a collection of expensive
OL,20,FJellycat toys without paying.
