OL,6,FThroughout August, he also targeted
OL,7,Fseveral supermarkets to steal electric
OL,8,Ftoothbrushes worth around #160 each.
OL,10,FFurther incidents were reported in
OL,11,FOctober, including the theft of a
OL,12,Fnumber of candles from the Neptune
OL,13,Fshowroom in Hove, and the theft of
OL,14,Fhealth products from Holland & Barrett
OL,15,Fin Brighton.
OL,17,FThorpe was arrested on 27 November and
OL,18,Fwas charged the following day with 11
OL,19,Fcounts of theft from a shop.
