OL,6,FHe appeared at Brighton Magistrates'
OL,7,FCourt on Saturday, 29 November, where
OL,8,Fhe pleaded guilty on all counts.
OL,10,FThorpe was sentenced the same day to
OL,11,F50 weeks in prison.
OL,13,FThe officer leading the investigation,
OL,14,FTimothy Carr-Dean, said: "Thorpe
OL,15,Frepeatedly stole high-value items
OL,16,Fwithout any regard for the impact on
OL,17,Fbusinesses.
OL,19,F"His actions caused financial loss,
OL,20,Fdisruption to staff, and a great deal
OL,21,Fof frustration for those affected.
